            <div type="translation">
                <p>My hope is the God, my refuge is the Christ, my protection is the Holy Spirit.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is taken from the hymn of the Akathistos Mass. Althought there is a paraphase. Instead of the nouns πατήρ and υἱός, the painter uses the names Θεός and Χριστός respectively.</p>
            </div>
